{"id": 1901, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都受不了哪些关于“有趣”的误解？", "description": "生活研究所不定期会推出当季应景并充满正义感的“无！法！忍！受！”小调查，欢迎来表态。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 11632, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170911171708GEtqWef1xYUZLNP9.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-11T17:00:14Z", "questions": [{"id": 2954, "title": "你都受不了哪些关于“有趣”的误解？", "content": "你都无法忍受哪些关于“有趣”的误解？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 234817, "content": "自嗨当有趣，我听这么牛逼的歌我为啥没对象啥的", "image": "img/option/option/20170911175831SNOUZQgeDKhfsz3F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234818, "content": "抢沙发、用流行语抢热评强行有趣", "image": "img/option/option/20170911173609rDPvq0jmRdYWCTsl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234819, "content": "跟风满屏666，绿罐旺仔牛奶自称“原谅绿”", "image": "img/option/option/201709111739036utmoIpscqSn9Mde.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234820, "content": "歧视当有趣，说女同事和自己有分歧是因为“快来大姨妈了”", "image": "img/option/option/20170911174010H9xKkmPbCd8juZGq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234821, "content": "浅薄当有趣，“严肃作品我看不来，我看书只求有趣”", "image": "img/option/option/20170911174024pGs9oecEtObK1X4g.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234824, "content": "把有趣视为一种工具，有趣是婚姻春药，职场润滑剂", "image": "img/option/option/20170911175006LFcSndo1ZhkPB5Xs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234825, "content": "认为有趣可以通过 1234 套路速成，传授有趣大法", "image": "img/option/option/20170911175026Cp38oPcsZbEB1ynX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 234822, "content": "认识有趣的人就是有趣了，交了那么多有趣朋友我也算有趣俱乐部的一员", "image": "img/option/option/20170911173921fbuz4rBHGVWp9PYO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}